Class BindingImpl

java.lang.Object
  impl.BindingImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Binding
public class BindingImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Binding

Implementation of the bindings used by Nanocontainer to link a BeanType (Interface or Class and Qualifier annotations) with an implementation (Class).

Author:
Matthieu Clochard
